{"tid":1932913,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"木村大女心美入行 登封面宣佈做音樂人","createTime":"2020-03-19T03:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T01:47:00.000Z","uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f66d4e6b9f80aa0354105daad25eae744a9a4d27","tid":1932913,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:55:52.000Z","msg":"日劇天王木村自從成為星爸後，與工藤靜香及細女光希（Koki）均成話題人物，木村與靜香多年來悉心培育兩個寶貝女成才，18歲大女心美（Cocomi）今日終於正式宣佈入行，令木村一家四口也成為圈中人。<br />\n<br />\n心美從3歲起學習提琴，11歲開始學吹長笛，剛畢業桐朋女子高校的她，希望成為音樂人，她擅長吹奏長笛，曾多次在音樂比賽上獲獎，一直盛傳有多間唱片公司密斟，望簽她出碟做歌手，月前她就為四重奏樂團擔任神秘表演嘉賓，如今出道即登上日版時裝雜誌《VOGUE》新一期之封面人物，還成為Dior的日本宣傳大使，繼妹妹光希（Koki）後入行。今次為心美拍攝封面的是國際人氣二人攝影師組合Luigi &amp; Iango，他們曾為名模Bella Hadid和奧斯卡影后珍妮花羅倫絲（Jennifer Lawrence）等巨星拍攝。有雜誌的工作人員指：「心美雖然第一次拍攝時裝雜誌有少少緊張，但亦能發放出最好的氣質。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200319/large/1584577639_dce6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200319%2Flarge%2F1584577639_dce6.jpg&h=23ae3231&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"355dac5563498c63506d589a4f5f92acaa495a71","tid":1932913,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:56:10.000Z","msg":"心美於今年三月畢業，四月開始就會入讀同系的音樂大學。有木村家的朋友爆料：「由於武漢肺炎疫情影響，令中學的畢業禮都要取消，心美感到很失望。她今後仍然會一邊學習吹笛，一邊在音樂界發展，這是不會變的。心美只想趁高中畢業，累積不同的經驗才決定今次為品牌擔任代言人。」<br />\n<br />\n木村、靜香視兩女為掌上明珠，心美比妹妹更有才華，除了音樂外，她亦對攝影充滿興趣，不時為妹妹充當攝影師拍攝靚相。大女心美出道，身為父母木村和靜香當然亦有祝賀，老竇木村就在微博上載兩個囡囡的合照，留言：「go FLY‼️my ANGELS‼️」，而靚媽靜香亦在IG上載她最愛的花束，留言感謝一直支持他們的所有人。"},{"pid":"f4beb5d3c2e364a44e0476c0fb24de64b827fc96","tid":1932913,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:56:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200319/large/1584577284_0ba9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200319%2Flarge%2F1584577284_0ba9.jpg&h=02af8af9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16487586537c37195086a30748ae6adc8527d242","tid":1932913,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:56:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2590000/2594605/90089513_493913968159500_1818666837774489998_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2590000%2F2594605%2F90089513_493913968159500_1818666837774489998_n_600.jpg&h=b9dc1626&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"027d22cf4d3b94e9a2076e96c81114f129fb4922","tid":1932913,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2590000/2594605/90091275_206554357226275_4552813218509892299_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2590000%2F2594605%2F90091275_206554357226275_4552813218509892299_n_600.jpg&h=be30ca8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"046dc5cfae886148c0906093fb2894f77e095868","tid":1932913,"uid":55519,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:57:59.000Z","msg":"家姐順眼咁多既"},{"pid":"d11043a8518902dff0e3aa7c53be4ef725403b3d","tid":1932913,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2590000/2594605/90088127_650292332448536_4615394796855421340_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2590000%2F2594605%2F90088127_650292332448536_4615394796855421340_n_600.jpg&h=1fcbe11f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"688fae06c1edb48b8493fb5ef5c110adabc6ee6b","tid":1932913,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T03:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200319/la