T06:24:27.000Z","msg":"講真兩姐妹都唔係超靚<br />\n不過星二代坐係度做kol都唔駛憂了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e78df79a0a420043ba5f63d77d7a25e9220a1f","tid":1932913,"uid":56716,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:34:47.000Z","msg":"我覺得光希靚好多，家姐個樣有啲腫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n曾經睇過Janice man出event同一班人影相，見到有個女仔好靚，頭細五官精緻，一眼睇落去覺得佢最靚（靚過jm），當時唔知邊個嚟，搵咗一輪先知原來係木村個女光希<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd9f2112fff78ce1c8a3555d57ec6de2507d33c","tid":1932913,"uid":55960,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:41:29.000Z","msg":"細妹成日著到/化到好老"},{"pid":"d7fa3247c60d217bdc87375684730a6a5fb298de","tid":1932913,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:31:59.000Z","msg":"3P要幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff3b665cde505fae9c5c601448e2b5746c288af","tid":1932913,"uid":8795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6943a39d4c57e4fea6747645a5f92fd8e352612c","tid":1932913,"uid":13616,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4bb6d5de1305d3900452c245c37f069bd57ae06c","tid":1932913,"uid":331590,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:03:29.000Z","msg":"好屈機GA基因,,,,唉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:24:27.000Z","msg":"講真兩姐妹都唔係超靚<br />\n不過星二代坐係度做kol都唔駛憂了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:14:48.000Z","msg":"一出就cover 其他model真係慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87893e24121b42349ffd2ae56b149a8b70bd3828","tid":1932913,"uid":32051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T01:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兩個女都一般貨色<br />\n屌你老母收皮好唔好<br />\n<br />\n<br /